{
  "stem": "4361.2",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 14.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Nothing, God forbid, could happen to them, which we were very nicely treated.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And although I remember I was very lonesome for my mother, for my mother very much so, and for my brothers, and all the goods things.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But somehow, there was such a wonderful intellectual ferment-- as I look back, I call it an 'intellectual ferment'-- in that school because we had such terrific teachers, that I became caught up with that And I stayed that way till March 1944.",
      "word_count": 43
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "March 1944 was the day that the Hungarian government, Horthy, the regent, and his government asked Adolf Eichmann to come into Hungary and take-- and take care-- [BACKGROUND NOISE] handle its Hungarian Jewish population.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And that is when everything turned to ashes, in a way.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Eichmann came in.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was in Kolozsvar, my last year just before going for the baccalaureate, which was supposed to take place in July, June, July.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We are in March.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And it was a terrible time for me and for my friend Susie because we were here and our parents were there.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Kolozsvar is in southern Transylvania.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Sighet is in northern Transylvania.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "About 400 miles, but in those days, the trains were not-- the tests were not very fast trains.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And it could have been a problem.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the problem was also, do we leave now or are we going to wait until we have our baccalaureate?",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Well, what happened-- and we called the families and the telephoning went back and forth.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Stay.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Graduate.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "No, come home.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "What happened was that the school itself changed the date.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And, you know, I mean, I think I had the easiest baccalaureate ever because the Nazis occupied the lower part of the school, and we were having our baccalaureate on the upper part of the school.",
      "word_count": 36
    }
  ],
